OL,3,CFirefighters tackle 200-tonne woodchip
OL,4,Cfire
OL,6,FA fire involving 200 tonnes of
OL,7,Fwoodchip broke out in Taunton
OL,8,Fovernight, with locals advised to keep
OL,9,Ftheir windows and doors closed for the
OL,10,Fremainder of the day.
OL,12,FAt its height, four fire engines and a
OL,13,Fwater bowser were at the scene of the
OL,14,Ffire on Ilminster Road just off the
OL,15,FA358, confirmed Devon and Somerset
OL,16,FFire and Rescue Service.
OL,18,FThe incident is ongoing, with two fire
OL,19,Fengines still in attendance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
