PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784467108
OL,3,CFirefighters tackle 200-tonne woodchip
OL,4,Cfire
OL,6,FThe fire started at 12.24am this
OL,7,Fmorning and involved 200 tonnes of
OL,8,Fwood and woodchip, creating a lot of
OL,9,Fsmoke in the area.
OL,11,FTeams from Taunton, Bridgewater,
OL,12,FWellington, Burnham on Sea, and
OL,13,FSomerset have worked with onsite staff
OL,14,Fto remove any unaffected wood chip.
